715096f.text:
Columbia University. Air view.
Its president, Dr. Butler, finds 8 in this country really justified in calling themselves universities.

The following was written on tracing paper over the photo: "Mr. Hughes - Note that dark veil has been run over all except central group of buildings. Please keep this contrast and make it even brighter in the central group if possible."
